Invocation Name: super chef
des:
Super Chef provides simple and healthy vegetarian recipes to make on the go. The recipes are included are:
Banana toast
Pitaya bowl
Oats
Channa Masala
Instant Noodles
Vegetable Stew
Semolina cake
Dosa

Enjoy!!
